{"tid":664174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警喬裝男客！按摩女手滑進內褲　一把握住下體","createTime":"2018-05-14T00:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T04:48:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"42bf3472d387fae673c1e42e82d265eaf35769d3","tid":664174,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:39:53.000Z","msg":"謝姓警員喬裝男客，到舒壓館逮半套性交易，替他按摩的周女將手伸進他內褲，抓住生殖器，謝隨即表明身分逮捕負責人。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，謝員當天佯裝男客到場查緝，羅女引導他到2樓，由周女負責按摩，起初很正常，後來周的手就從他肚子由上往下伸到內褲內，撫摸他生殖器，再一把抓住。謝表明警察身分，周女竟說「不小心碰到」，警方仍依法將負責人逮捕，周則依社維法裁處。<br />\n<br />\n張姓、羅姓負責人均矢口否認妨害風化犯行，法官不採信其證詞，認定2人未管控小姐行為，依共同圖利容留猥褻罪各判處有期徒刑5個月，得易科罰金15萬元。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180514/640_5f735f8400c1cb638350d655acd49826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180514%2F640_5f735f8400c1cb638350d655acd49826.jpg&h=6440dfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353269/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353269%2F&d=DUh6sihs39eOmPFGCy%2Fo5wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=37ff5277\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180514%2F1353269%2F&h=979b86ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180514/1353269/</a>"},{"pid":"2ff1822e455d84d7beff7b08e83a6bc188ce9d7f","tid":664174,"uid":56111,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:50:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所</span></span>"},{"pid":"8bffe80254316d436967e7de9abbecc18f488002","tid":664174,"uid":177219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T00:51:59.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"08d5ca053b7df7a8896a83ed7c4402539914a85c","tid":664174,"uid":146558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{